voltha-helm-charts
  - create a branch named voltha-2.12   v2.12
  - Update Chart.yaml (help and adapter charts) to 2.12.0

voltha-system-tests:
  - create branch voltha-2.12
  - create tag 2.12.0 on voltha-2.12 branch

** These two are the only ones who receive tag=2.12.0


For all other repos:
  o Create release tag 2.12.0
  o From release tag create branch voltha-2.12

Component repository VERSION FILE:
  o Increase minor version from 1.1.x to 1.2.0-dev


https://docs.voltha.org/master/release_notes/release_process.html
